{"tid":1243400,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"老實講，政府已經成功瓦解反對勢力","createTime":"2019-06-19T12:27:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T13:15:36.000Z","uid":227855,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ca121dadd57bfa36bd57e5a0a9cbc07d0e4b5549","tid":1243400,"uid":227855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T12:27:52.000Z","msg":"由星期一開始，班官每日推一個人出嚟開記招<br />\n<br />\n星期一：黑警一哥<br />\n星期二：林奠<br />\n星期三：比卡超<br />\n<br />\n輪住出嚟講廢話<br />\n你班網民就會出post屌柒佢<br />\n個FB就keep住洗版<br />\n<br />\n星期五升級嘅post？沖撚走晒啦<br />\n<br />\n佢哋出嚟見記者嘅schedule就係等你哋啲乜春三罷、deadline、升級、ultimatum全部谷唔起<br />\n<br />\n大家有眼睇啦<br />\n今個星期關於升級嘅討論<br />\n同之前612三罷嘅氣氛差幾撚遠<br />\n<br />\n得罪講句<br />\n今次政府真係好撚高招<br />\n出嚟講廢話俾人鬧幾句就occupy晒你哋啲eyeballs<br />\n反對勢力已經被瓦解<br />\n<br />\n不過，我歡迎大家prove me wrong<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xCA5yYE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxCA5yYE.png&h=b67965e7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XVkUsiF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXVkUsiF.png&h=c77bfaaf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aa6890df67c51bdbd499d1ac0d2b373034a96c58","tid":1243400,"uid":37596,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T12:32:23.000Z","msg":"最重要係<br />\n1)立法會唔開會<br />\n2)特首高官唔返政總唔返工<br />\n香港市民根本無地方可攻, 620/621已完<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自斷相臂又點斬手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08798fb32a8174b96d322e35c224f64d802621e8","tid":1243400,"uid":227855,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"aa6890df67c51bdbd499d1ac0d2b373034a96c58","tid":1243400,"uid":37596,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T12:32:23.000Z","msg":"最重要係<br />\n1)立法會唔開會<br />